OL,3,CBollywood singer Asha Bhosle dies at 92
OL,5,FAsha Bhosle, one of India's most
OL,6,Fversatile Bollywood singers whose
OL,7,Fperformances shaped the country's
OL,8,Fmusical memory and modern cinema, has
OL,9,Fdied at the age of 92.
OL,11,FThe singer was admitted to a hospital
OL,12,Fin Mumbai, suffering exhaustion and a
OL,13,Fchest infection, where she later died
OL,14,Ffrom multiple organ failure, according
OL,15,Fto Pratit Samdani, a physician at
OL,16,FBreach Candy hospital.
