OL,3,CBollywood singer Asha Bhosle dies at 92
OL,5,FWith a career spanning more than eight
OL,6,Fdecades, her work earned her two
OL,7,FNational Film Awards, seven Filmfare
OL,8,FAwards for Best Female Playback
OL,9,FSinger, and the Dadasaheb Phalke Award
OL,10,Fin 2000 - India's highest honour in
OL,11,Fcinema.
OL,13,FShe recorded close to 12,000 songs,
OL,14,Fboldly embracing cabaret and Western-
OL,15,Finfluenced melodies to forge a
OL,16,Fdistinct musical identity that stood
OL,17,Funiquely apart from her sister, Lata
OL,18,FMangeshkar, herself a legendary voice
OL,19,Frevered as the "Melody Queen."
