OL,3,CBollywood singer Asha Bhosle dies at 92
OL,5,FBorn on Sept. 8, 1933, Asha Bhosle was
OL,6,Finitiated into music by her father
OL,7,FDinanath Mangeshkar, who was also a
OL,8,Ftrained singer. All four of her
OL,9,Fsiblings became accomplished singers
OL,10,Fand musicians.
OL,12,FHer popularity led to her name being
OL,13,Fgiven a nod in the British band
OL,14,FCornershop's 1997 hit Brimful of Asha.
OL,16,FTributes have been made by fans and
OL,17,Fworld leaders.
OL,19,FWriting on X, Indian Prime Minister
OL,20,FNarendra Modi said he was "deeply
OL,21,Fsaddened by (her) passing".
