OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776003065
OL,3,CBollywood singer Asha Bhosle dies at 92
OL,5,FModi described her as "one of India's
OL,6,Fmost renowned and versatile voices",
OL,7,Fadding, "her unique musical journey
OL,8,Fspanning decades has enriched our
OL,9,Fcultural heritage and touched the
OL,10,Fhearts of countless people around the
OL,11,Fworld."
OL,13,FShe is survived by her son Anand
OL,14,FBhosle, who announced her deathm, and
OL,15,Fher granddaughter Zanai Bhosle, who
OL,16,Ffollowed her into music and remained
OL,17,Fby her side in her final years.
OL,19,FHer last rites are due to be performed
OL,20,Fin Mumbai's Shivaji Park on April 13.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
